  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3576690/extras/380df731200c556e0f25770e93b2323a.avif?t=1766482121\" width=574 height=144 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Last Laugh</strong> is a horror game with <strong>7 different endings</strong>.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>STORY:</strong><br>The game follows three mischievous teenagers who enjoy hanging out, laughing, and playing games at one of their friends' houses. But then...</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3576690/extras/5ae8b5e8ce51452c1c045402e5650a6d.poster.avif?t=1766482121\" width=350 height=262 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3576690/extras/5ae8b5e8ce51452c1c045402e5650a6d.webm?t=1766482121\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3576690/extras/5ae8b5e8ce51452c1c045402e5650a6d.mp4?t=1766482121\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Features:</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🎮 <strong>Retro Horror Experience</strong> – Immerse yourself in a horror atmosphere with <strong>PS1-style graphics</strong> and <strong>pixel art visuals</strong> that enhance the eerie feeling.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🔄 <strong>Multiple Endings</strong> – Uncover all <strong>7 different endings</strong>!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >📺 <strong>Dynamic Menu Changes</strong> – The <strong>main menu evolves</strong> based on the endings you've unlocked.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >💾 <strong>Auto-Save Feature</strong> – Your progress is automatically saved, allowing you to <strong>continue and explore different endings</strong> without starting over!</p></li></ul>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3576690/extras/380df731200c556e0f25770e93b2323a.avif?t=1766482121\" width=574 height=144 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Last Laugh</strong> is a horror game with <strong>7 different endings</strong>.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>STORY:</strong><br>The game follows three mischievous teenagers who enjoy hanging out, laughing, and playing games at one of their friends' houses. But then...</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3576690/extras/5ae8b5e8ce51452c1c045402e5650a6d.poster.avif?t=1766482121\" width=350 height=262 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3576690/extras/5ae8b5e8ce51452c1c045402e5650a6d.webm?t=1766482121\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3576690/extras/5ae8b5e8ce51452c1c045402e5650a6d.mp4?t=1766482121\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Features:</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🎮 <strong>Retro Horror Experience</strong> – Immerse yourself in a horror atmosphere with <strong>PS1-style graphics</strong> and <strong>pixel art visuals</strong> that enhance the eerie feeling.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🔄 <strong>Multiple Endings</strong> – Uncover all <strong>7 different endings</strong>!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >📺 <strong>Dynamic Menu Changes</strong> – The <strong>main menu evolves</strong> based on the endings you've unlocked.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >💾 <strong>Auto-Save Feature</strong> – Your progress is automatically saved, allowing you to <strong>continue and explore different endings</strong> without starting over!</p></li></ul>",
